proval authority, not yet pre-briefed", "role": "Economic Buyer", "title": "CFO and board (members not named)", "sentiment": "Unknown \u2014 never engaged directly", "last_contact_date": null}, {"name": "IT and Digital Board (members not named)", "risk": "If Jonas presents a neutral three-vendor bake-off to the board without a pre-sold Zycus recommendation, the board may choose on price or ERP-native fit instead of AI maturity. The board presentation must be scheduled in July\u2013Aug to meet a Q3 decision window\u2014if it slips to Q4, the May 2026 go-live is unrecoverable and urgency dies.", "role": "Decision Maker", "title": "Board (CFO, IT, business leads)", "sentiment": "Unknown\u2014the board has not been engaged. Jonas stated 25 Nov 'the recommendation that the team does need to go to an IT and Digital Board where our CFO is involved\u2026 making the final decision of each of these projects.' The board presentation is the final approval gate but is not yet scheduled as of 30 Jun 2026.", "last_contact_date": null}, {"name": "Jonas Elber", "risk": "Owns CLM recommendation but lacks unilateral board authority", "role": "Champion", "title": "Head of Technology (formerly Procurement Innovation & Technology Lead)", "sentiment": "Positive, advocating internally", "last_contact_date": "2026-04-27"}, {"name": "Anthony Gray", "risk": "N/A", "role": "Coach", "title": "VP (Zycus, deal owner's manager)", "sentiment": "Driving commercial close (Zycus-side)", "last_contact_date": "2026-04-27"}, {"name": "Nickolaj Almskou Holler", "risk": "Bridge to the board but quiet since Nov 2025", "role": "Influencer", "title": "Director, Global Business Services & Transformation", "sentiment": "Evaluating; requested references, pricing, sandbox", "last_contact_date": "2025-11-27"}]}, "meddpicc": {"metrics": {"status": "partial", "sources": ["Avoma discovery 2025-10-29 (Jonas Elber)", "Avoma alignment 2025-11-20 (Jonas Elber)", "SF Business_Objectives__c"], "narrative": "The buyer artic